    "body": "Can you clone the truffle repository from source, and then install from there? The non-released version of Truffle has the solc version bumped to 0.1.6.\n\n```\n$ npm uninstall -g truffle\n$ git clone https://github.com/ConsenSys/truffle.git\n$ cd truffle\n$ npm install -g .\n```\n\nShould work for you. Will release a new version soon.\n",
